   <text>
      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> 918/5 </s>
               <s> Visto Rev.Stampa - Milano 1920</s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>[Coppia su slittino]</head>
               <figDesc> Una coppia su di uno slittino in mezzo alla neve
               </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            S. Felice lì 27/4 1918</s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p type="retro">
                     <lb/>            Oliva mia, <lb/>            trovarmi da tre giorni a letto <lb/>            con febbre e forte catarro bron - <lb/>            chiale, domani tenterò di alzarmi.  <lb/>            Ormai la fase acuta è pasfata.<lb/>            Qui in questo <gap reason="illegible"/> paese respira  <lb/>            cattiva aria per me e forse anche <lb/>            per molti altri, piove, piove e piove <lb/>            sempre. Mi sento tanto stanco <lb/>            e avvilito, come non mai ho  <lb/>            la nostalgia di tante cose belle e <lb/>            il desiderio d'amore purisfimo, <lb/>            d'un tuo sguardo, d'un tuo sospiro.  <lb/>            Baci </p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <lb/>tuo <signed>
                     <persName>
                        <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                     </persName>
                  </signed>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="address-destination">
               <p>
                  <address>
                     <addrLine>
                        <lb/>            Gent Sig na <lb/>            Oliva Turtura <lb/>            Via Girolamo Rosfi 58 <lb/>            Ravenna </addrLine>
                  </address>
               </p>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext" part="N">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 224 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
